    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition vehicle that presents beautifully and should appeal to someone looking for a standout example rather than an average driver. It runs and drives extremely well, feels tight and well-kept, and shows the kind of care you want to see in a top-tier car. Inside and out, it is unusually clean and well preserved, with only the sort of minor age-related signs a careful buyer might expect on close inspection. A very strong, honest example that should satisfy someone wanting a vehicle they can be proud to own and enjoy right away.",
