    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Value-priced and ready for its next owner, this vehicle is a practical option for anyone seeking affordable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age, but offers straightforward utility, a comfortable cabin, and the kind of price point that makes sense for budget-conscious buyers. If you want an inexpensive way to get on the road without overpaying, this is a smart one to see in person.",
