    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Clean, honest driver with solid mechanical character and plenty of life left for the next owner. The engine pulls well, the transmission does its job, and it\u2019s the kind of affordable car that still feels usable day to day. Not a showpiece, but it has the right bones: dependable startup, good road manners, and the kind of straightforward platform that\u2019s easy to live with and easy to wrench on. A great budget buy for someone who wants practical transportation with some substance instead of paying up for cosmetics.",
      "price": 7900.0,
