    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Built for the buyer who sees possibility where others just see a parked car, this ride has a gritty, honest character that stands out in a world of polished clones. It\u2019s the kind of vehicle that could be a budget daily, a hands-on weekend project, or a dependable spare to keep around when life calls for something ready to work. There\u2019s real personality here, and for the right owner, it offers affordable entry into ownership with plenty of room to make it your own.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "A practical, budget-friendly vehicle that offers straightforward transportation at an accessible price. Best suited for buyers seeking affordable mobility, a starter car, or a project with potential. Priced to reflect its condition while still delivering solid value for the money, this is a smart opportunity for someone who wants dependable basics without a big upfront cost.",
      "price": 5950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this car would make a great project, parts donor, or inexpensive runaround for the right buyer. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s an honest vehicle with plenty of usable life and a lot to offer someone handy or looking for a low-cost option. If you want something affordable and don\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC, this could be a really worthwhile buy.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
