      "timestep_posted": 40
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project with a strong-running engine, responsive transmission, and a chassis that still feels eager on the road. This car shows its age cosmetically, but it offers a great foundation for someone who wants affordable transportation or a hands-on build. Starts, runs, and moves out well, with plenty of usable life left for the next owner willing to sort the details. If you know how to turn a wrench, this is a chance to get into a capable car at a sensible price.",
